1. What is one of the challenges that sales reps face when trying to close deals?
Ans: A. Losing deals to delays

2. How does Einstein Opportunity Scoring help reps close deals?
Ans: D. Assigns scores to different opportunities based on org data so reps can prioritize deals

3. What types of insights are available with Opportunity Insights?
Ans: D. All of the above
A. Key moments
B. Follow-up reminders
C. Deal predictions
